---
description: USE WHEN mapping a Future to widgets, adding timeouts, JSON-encoding maps off the UI thread, or filtering nulls from lists or iterables. Prefer kartal future.ext, map.ext, list.ext, iterable.exts.
globs:
  - "**/*.dart"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Kartal async & collections

| Pattern | kartal |
|---------|--------|
| Manual `FutureBuilder` states | `future.ext.toBuild(onSuccess:, loadingWidget:, notFoundWidget:, onError:, data:)` |
| `timeout` + log + null | `future.ext.timeoutOrNull(...)` |
| Heavy `jsonEncode(map)` | `map.ext.safeJsonEncodeCompute()` |
| Remove nulls | `iterable.exts.makeSafe()` / `makeSafeCustom` |
| Nullable list checks / index | `list?.ext.isNullOrEmpty`, `ext.indexOrNull(...)` |

See `ai/claude/kartal-async-future/SKILL.md`.
